Kafka Streaming Usecases:

rdbms data into HDFS/Hive
-------------------
commit log -> flume -> kafka -> flume -> hive/hdfs


rdbms to Hbase/Nosql/Rdbms
commit log -> flume -> kafka -> Kafka java consumer -> write Java Api of nosql db/rdbms

machine data into Hive by cleaning the data::
-----------------------------------
kafka java producer -> kafka -> spark streaming -> Hive/Hdfs
----------------------------------------------------------------
Apache Nifi -> capture event data.



